<section class="section" id="about" style="padding-top: 60px; padding-bottom: 60px;">
  <div class="container" style="padding-left: 40px; padding-right: 100px;">
    <div class="row align-items-center" id="counter">
      <div class="col-md-12 mt-4 pt-2 mt-sm-0 pt-sm-0">
        <div class="ms-lg-5">
          <div class="section-title">
            <h3 class="title mb-4">
              About Architecture &amp; Interior Design Excellence Awards &amp; Conference 2025 - Hyatt Centric , Candolim , Goa ( Global&nbsp;Edition)
            </h3>
            <p class="text-muted" align="justify"> 
              The Interior and Architecture Awards and Conference National Edition is going to reward Interior Designers, Architects, Designing studios, Interior and Architecture firms, organizations in design world. These Awards are going to be a small token of appreciation for the individuals who are going to make an honorable future of this society.
            </p>
            <p class="text-muted" align="justify">
              All the visionaries who wish to enhance, grow, share, gain and boost within the walls of success and Industrial competition may participate at this conference. It is a great opportunity to bring together an entire community of great Designers, Architects and Creative Minds. It will motivate other great minds to strive towards aphelion.
            </p>
            <p class="text-muted" align="justify">
              The Awards ceremony will be organized on <b>13th June 2025  at Hyatt Centric , Candolim , Goa ( Global&nbsp;Edition).</b> The conference is expected to be honored by ingenious bureaucrats, Global industrial leaders, Top CEOs and Politicians.
            </p>
            <p class="text-muted" align="justify">
              This Ceremony will be presented on various digital landscapes of Social media and news sites. It will be covered by well-known electronic and print media houses and the entire function will be uploaded on Media Websites.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<% event = EventDetail.last %>

<section class="event-schedule-section py-5 text-center position-relative" style="background: url('<%= asset_path('world_map.jpg') %>') no-repeat center center / cover; padding-bottom: 60px">

  <div class="position-absolute top-0 start-0 w-100 h-100" style="background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.93); z-index: 0;"></div>

  <div class="position-relative container" style="z-index: 1;">
    <h2 class="mb-5 fw-bold">Event Schedule &amp; Venue</h2>

    <div class="row justify-content-center g-4">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded text-center h-100">
          <div class="d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center rounded bg-primary bg-opacity-10 shadow-sm" style="width: 60px; height: 60px;">
            <i class="bi bi-calendar-event fs-4 text-primary"></i>
          </div>
          <h5 class="mt-3 fw-semibold">Event Date</h5>
          <p class="text-primary mb-0"><%= event.event_date.strftime("%-d %B %Y") %></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded text-center h-100">
          <div class="d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center rounded bg-primary bg-opacity-10 shadow-sm" style="width: 60px; height: 60px;">
            <i class="bi bi-geo-alt fs-4 text-primary"></i>
          </div>
          <h5 class="mt-3 fw-semibold">Venue</h5>
          <p class="text-primary mb-0"><%= event.venue %></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded text-center h-100">
          <div class="d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center rounded bg-primary bg-opacity-10 shadow-sm" style="width: 60px; height: 60px;">
            <i class="bi bi-clock fs-4 text-primary"></i>
          </div>
          <h5 class="mt-3 fw-semibold">Nomination Deadline</h5>
          <p class="text-primary mb-0"><%= event.nomination_deadline.strftime("%-d %B %Y") %></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <a href="/nomination" class="btn btn-primary mt-5 px-4 py-2 fs-5">
      Nominate Now <i class="bi bi-arrow-right ms-2"></i>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

